### DocCentric API Test File
### Use with JetBrains HTTP Client or convert to curl

### Health Check
GET http://localhost:8000/health

### Root Endpoint
GET http://localhost:8000/

### Create Patient (Bangla)
POST http://localhost:8000/api/patients
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "রোগী ১",
  "age": 45,
  "gender": "পুরুষ",
  "phone": "+8801712345678",
  "email": "patient@example.com",
  "address": "ঢাকা, বাংলাদেশ",
  "blood_type": "B+",
  "allergies": "কোনো অ্যালার্জি নেই",
  "emergency_contact": "+8801812345678"
}

### List All Patients
GET http://localhost:8000/api/patients

### Get Patient by ID
GET http://localhost:8000/api/patients/1

### Update Patient
PUT http://localhost:8000/api/patients/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "আপডেট রোগী",
  "age": 50,
  "phone": "+8801712345679"
}

### Delete Patient
DELETE http://localhost:8000/api/patients/2

### Create Visit
POST http://localhost:8000/api/visits
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "patient_id": 1,
  "doctor_id": "DR001",
  "chief_complaint": "মাথা ব্যথা এবং জ্বর",
  "symptoms": "৩ দিন ধরে উচ্চ জ্বর",
  "diagnosis": "সর্দি",
  "tests": "রক্ত পরীক্ষা",
  "prescription": "প্যারাসিটামল ৫০০মি.গ্রা.",
  "suggestions": "বিশ্রাম এবং পানি পান করুন",
  "notes": "৫ দিন পরে ফলো আপ",
  "visit_type": "initial"
}

### Get Visit
GET http://localhost:8000/api/visits/1

### Get Patient Visits
GET http://localhost:8000/api/patients/1/visits

### Upload Audio (Bangla conversation)
### Note: Requires actual audio file
POST http://localhost:8000/api/upload-audio
Content-Type: multipart/form-data

doctor_id: DR001
audio_file: @sample_conversation.mp3

### Upload Audio with curl
### curl -X POST "http://localhost:8000/api/upload-audio" \
###   -F "doctor_id=DR001" \
###   -F "audio_file=@sample_conversation.mp3"

### Check Ollama Connection
### curl http://localhost:11434/api/tags
